          <br/><br/>
          We want to inform you that <strong>your library platform</strong> will undergo scheduled maintenance.
        </mj-text>

        <!-- Maintenance Info -->
        <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#555">
          <strong>Date:</strong> {{maintenanceDate}}<br/>
          <strong>Time:</strong> {{maintenanceTime}}<br/>
          <strong>Expected Downtime:</strong> {{downtimeEstimate}}
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text>
          During this time, access to the library site and services may be temporarily unavailable. We appreciate your patience and understanding as we work to improve performance and reliability.
        </mj-text>

